title: BuildBox 2.1.1 Build 1179
description:
Make games without programming. Buildbox is a breakthrough game creation experience. Creating games is as easy as dropping images into the software, making changes to their properties and hitting play. Every tool you need to complete your game is included inside Buildbox. You have access to complete management of your assets, integrated level editor, game menu system, advanced ad and in app purchase solution, font editor, gameplay settings and more.For the first time, anyone can make games without having a technical bone in their body. Buildbox lets you make games as easy as a powerpoint presentation.

ystem Requirements

    Windows 7 or Windows 8 or Windows 10
    Intel Core 2 Duo CPU (or AMD equivalent)
    200MB free disk space (for the software only)
    1GB RAM
